<p>These utility classes help you control <strong>horizontal
layout</strong> (<code>flex-direction: row</code>) and horizontal
alignment (<code>justify-content</code>) using simple and expressive
class names.</p>
<p>They use <code>display: flex</code> and align items along the main
(horizontal) axis.</p>
