<h3 id="flex-grow-utilities">Flex Grow Utilities</h3>
<p>Control how flexible a flex item should grow relative to the rest of
the items with <code>.grow-{n}</code> classes.</p>
<h4 id="basic-syntax-1">Basic Syntax</h4>
<pre class="html"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;grow-{n}&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
<ul>
<li><code>{n}</code> is a number between <code>0</code> and
<code>7</code></li>
<li>Maps to <code>flex-grow: n</code></li>
</ul>
