<h3 id="gap-utilities">Gap Utilities</h3>
<p>The <code>.gap-*</code> utility classes let you quickly control the
spacing between flex or grid items using a consistent spacing scale.</p>
<p>They apply the native CSS <code>gap</code> property, which works with
both flex and grid containers.</p>
<h4 id="basic-syntax-2">Basic Syntax</h4>
<pre class="html"><code>&lt;div class=&quot;gap-{n}&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
<ul>
<li><code>{n}</code> is a number between <code>0</code> and
<code>7</code></li>
</ul>
